1 STATE OF OKLAHOMA
2 2nd Session of the 60th Legislature (2026)
3 HOUSE BILL 3623 By: Lawson
4
5
6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to State Capitol security; creating
the Oklahoma State Capitol Security Act of 2026;
8 providing for noncodification; and providing an
effective date.
9
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
14 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
15 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma State
16 Capitol Security Act of 2026".
17 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
